VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT CFLAGS\s*=.*\b(-fno-stack-protector|-z execstack)\b
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:-fno-stack-protector|-D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=0|-z\s+execstack|--no-pie|-fno-pie|-fno-aslr
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure compiler flags that disable security protections.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Compiler Flags.
